OL,6,FAs victims and their families wait for
OL,7,Fthe report into the infected blood
OL,8,Fscandal to be published, ITV News West
OL,9,Fof England Reporter Sangita Lal heard
OL,10,Fabout the impact its had from three of
OL,11,Fthe survivors
OL,13,FBirchgrove Memorial is tucked away
OL,14,Fdown a long gravel path surrounded by
OL,15,Fovergrown woodland near Swindon.
OL,17,FIt is a place that recognises what
OL,18,Fhappened to so many affected by the
OL,19,Finfected blood scandal, and what so
OL,20,Fmany lost.
