OL,6,FThe entrance of the garden is marked
OL,7,Fby a stone inscribed with the words:
OL,8,F"Birchgrove - This grove celebrates
OL,9,Fthe lives of the 1,200 people with
OL,10,FHaemophilia infected with HIV."
OL,12,FNow though most of the trees represent
OL,13,Fsomeone who's died.
OL,15,FAlan Burgess is a haemophiliac who was
OL,16,Finfected with HIV and Hepatitis C 40
OL,17,Fyears ago at 27-years-old.
OL,19,FAs he showed me around the garden he
OL,20,Fpointed at a number of trees.
