OL,6,F"I mean I come here. I see my friends
OL,7,FGareth, Hayden, I see Caddy, I see
OL,8,FPaul... I've lost them," Alan said.
OL,10,F"I've lost them over the years and I
OL,11,Fmiss them so much now. We loved each
OL,12,Fother because we were blood brothers."
OL,14,FAlan created the garden in 1996 hoping
OL,15,Fto create a living and lasting tribute
OL,16,Fto those whose lives had been changed
OL,17,Fby receiving contaminated blood.
