OL,7,Finfected with Hepatitus A, B and C
OL,8,Fafter having two wisdom teeth out when
OL,9,Fhe was 12. He was diagnosed in 1990
OL,10,Fafter becoming increasingly ill and
OL,11,Fjaundiced.
