OL,6,FSue says she encouraged him to get a
OL,7,Fblood transfusion that infected him
OL,8,Fwith HIV.
OL,10,FHe was diagnosed in 1985 and died five
OL,11,Fyears later.
OL,13,F"I've always felt guilty. I've always
OL,14,Ffelt guilty that I made him go to the
OL,15,Fhospital. I will never forgive myself
OL,16,Ffor that," Sue said.
OL,18,FIt's a scandal hidden for 40 years.
OL,20,FAnd many affected will not see the
OL,21,Fjustice that next week might bring.
